short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Get ad data from Google Ads Transparency.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AdUnveil is a powerful Chrome extension that augments Google Ads Transparency Center, empowering marketers and researchers with valuable insights. Only Youtube ads are supported at this time.
